1. run docker-compose up -d MailHog
2. Follow the steps here: https://kinsta.com/blog/mailhog/
3. Test it by writing the folloing code:
    mhsendmail test@mailhog.local <<EOF
> From: H <kinsta@mailhog.local>
> To: test <test@mailhog.local>
> Subject: Playing
> 
> Hello, this was a test
> 
> See you
> EOF
